{"tid":1636619,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[被迫罷工核彈] 僱員冇保險開工=僱主犯法","createTime":"2019-10-07T19:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T01:52:57.000Z","uid":222747,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0385949f82147d686755bba2020c39a271ab36b2","tid":1636619,"uid":222747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:01:00.000Z","msg":"基本法241章《緊急情況規例條例》第2條<br />\n2.訂立規例的權力<br />\n(1)在行政長官會同行政會議認為屬<span style=\"color: red;\">緊急情況或危害公安的情況</span>時，行政長官會同行政會議可訂立任何他認為合乎公眾利益的規例。<br />\n<br />\nAIA團體保險簡介:<br />\n意外保障之不保事項<br />\r\n1. 不論神智清醒與否，自殺或企圖自致之傷害。<br />\r\n2. 不論宣戰與否之戰爭、革命或任何軍事行動。<br />\r\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\">暴動及民事騷亂</span>、罷工或恐怖主義活動。<br />\r\n4. 抵觸或企圖抵觸法律的行為，又或是拒捕。<br />\n<br />\n基本法第282章 《僱員補償條例》第40條<br />\n40.對僱主的法律責任承保的強制保險<br />\n(1)除第(1B)及(1C)款另有規定外，<span style=\"color: red;\">除非有關於任何僱員有一份由保險人所發出的有效保險單</span>，而該保險單就僱主的法律責任承保的款額不小於附表4所指明的適用款額，<span style=\"color: red;\">否則僱主不得僱用該僱員從事任何工作。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">簡單一句：香港緊急法實施後，好多保險都唔包；而僱傭補償條例需要僱員受到保險保障先可以開工。僱主喺個僱員冇保險嘅情況之下都要番工好有機會犯咗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">頭盔：有極少數保險係有包</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家朝早番工記得問下老闆幫自己同公司買嗰份保險而家仲有冇效呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"7eaee9061644fd5d46f3c2f1074be86ff2cc7389","tid":1636619,"uid":222747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b15e551afbe4827e591c61863795143777764088","tid":1636619,"uid":222747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751af1c8441648f60d4795d3dd70e7a3869dfe95","tid":1636619,"uid":222747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:05:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938f16d236b25648da630eae123264f3f3ebdc64","tid":1636619,"uid":49300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:10:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15afa9057a361371effd9ae23e83f715d34d2d3b","tid":1636619,"uid":222747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:11:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7734adde721f73c787be6ee2ba909847bc15c6","tid":1636619,"uid":57929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:14:59.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n病左帶口罩返工<br />\n點知遇上濫捕popo比狗打<br />\n咁咪仆街？？"},{"pid":"aaa333c4b9c76deb09fb2d63d5b0c644b84fc432","tid":1636619,"uid":51293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:15:37.000Z","msg":"有效實有效<br />\n但現時情況唔包有得claim"},{"pid":"870a26bfe304a015b77449d8cd370bf0e69ce190","tid":1636619,"uid":222747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T22:52:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa359db60785cc7b110ceca45b31a404840bea0c","tid":1636619,"uid":222747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T23:03:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c2a5f28aa5b55f331b3e864aa8ef943357a153","tid":1636619,"uid":222747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T23